    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Balticranocapsus aleksanderi sp. nov., holotype (CNUHHMF006). A, dorsal habitus. B, C, lateral habitus. D, head, pronotum and scutellum. E, antennae. F, hind tarsus. G, claw. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
